Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:00:58.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368.513,500)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, love
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸会处理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.55,0:01:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy's going to make it all right
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冷静下来  乖女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:20.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  珍珍怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:37.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, what's wrong with Pearl?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她那个烂舞伴放了她鸽子  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Her scurvy prom date stood her up, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在她又没法另外再找一个舞伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now she can't seem to find another
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为他是全海洋里唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.41,0:01:45.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because there's only one fish in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.12,0:01:49.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又高又帅  肤色又古铜的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:49.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long, tan, and handsome as he is
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非他不可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that's him
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more crying
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会给你找个舞伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll get you a date
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.21,0:01:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我陪你去舞会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What about Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就让海绵宝宝陪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, take SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fry cook?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道那样会怎么影响我气质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:14.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what that would do to my complexion?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人会把我误认成天文馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People will mistake me for a planetarium
Dialogue: 1,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我就是不能带他去  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't take him, daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们会把我踢出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll kick me off
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,年鉴委员会常驻人员的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:25.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the most frequently pictured
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the yearbook committee
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.21,0:02:28.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:28.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they would
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须再找个别人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to find someone else
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们当中有哪个幸运儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which one of you lucky lubbers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要陪我可爱女儿珍珍参加舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wants to take me lovely daughter pearl to the prom?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别迟到了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:45.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just don't be late, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now listen, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我指望着你把今晚变成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a-counting on you to make this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为特别的女孩打造的特别的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a very special night for a very special girl
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要记住  你这全都是为了蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, you're doing it for good old Mr.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是在跟我做的假人说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you talking to that dummy I made?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很逼真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's pretty realistic, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这部位的材料是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:04.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I made this part out of
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管了  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你陪珍珍参加舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're taking Pearl to her prom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是舞会专家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am a prom expert
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  我是舞会废物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gary, I'm a prom failure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我连自己的初中舞会都找不到舞伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:20.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even get a date for my own junior prom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  让妈妈当舞伴的是派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, that was Patrick who brought his mom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且我又怎么能比得上珍珍的前男友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, how am I supposed to compare with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl's old boyfriend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又高又帅皮肤古铜先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Long, tan and handsome?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you have?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, Gary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.23,0:03:40.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336.468,350)}又高又帅\N肤色古铜
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.44,0:03:39.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这本杂志让我想到办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:39.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This magazine gives me an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Long
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,皮肤古铜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tan
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了小蜗  就等珍珍看到我这身了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary, wait till Pearl gets an eyeful of this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得怎么样  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Pearl?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打理得真的还不错  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cleans up pretty good, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码没人会认得出你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least no one will recognize you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想熬过这场舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just want to get through this dance
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且保住我的社交地位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with my social status intact
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想参加舞会  拍完我的照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to go to the prom, get my picture taken
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想跳舞  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I want to dance, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想跟朋友一起喝潘趣酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna drink punch with my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也不要做你平常做的其他事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't do that other thing you're always doing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  得上豪车了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, we got to get back to the limo
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,豪车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A limo
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么不早说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好爱豪车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love limousines
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对他宽容点  小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go easy on him, lassie
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可没钱再另外请个煎炸厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:04.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't afford to break in a new fry cook
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(853.187,192)}体育馆  舞会之夜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这体育馆看着真是好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The gym looks wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.67,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(927.29,166)}出口
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们应该做的第一件事就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess the first thing we should do is
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的第一张舞会照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My first prom picture
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的第一张舞会照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:30.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our first prom picture
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把事先成了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过来吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be right there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能不能快点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:41.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Will you hurry up?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a second
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I am
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheese
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,值得留作纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That will be a keeper
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看  是珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, it's Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我朋友来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, here come my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去给我打点潘趣酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:06.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go get me some punch
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舞会专家  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prom expert, away
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:11.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, girls
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想带你认识一下比利鱼金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to meet Billy Fishkins
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,认识数学课上的那个比目鱼布莱恩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know Bryan Flounder from math class
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  布莱恩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Bryan
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的舞伴在哪  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like, where's your date, Pearl?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们好想见见他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're dying to meet him
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在潘趣酒碗那边打潘趣酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's over at the punch bowl getting me some punch
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个高个子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he the really tall one?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:36.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快  去看看辛迪的裙子有多丑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:07:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick, let's go see how ugly Cindy's dress is
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.06,0:07:02.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:02.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, it won't bite
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look ridiculous
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:16.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快蹲下  我们会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:18.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get down, they'll see us
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的前男友  屋大维霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my ex-boyfriend, Octavius Rex
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又名又高又帅皮肤古铜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,aka Long, tan and handsome
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过他肯定保不住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I bet he isn't holder
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地方浪漫舞大赛奖杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the regional romantic dance championship trophy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:35.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that back
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That didn't just happen
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:42.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:47.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不出来大家都在跳碰撞舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see everybody here is doing the whack?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,碰撞舞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whack?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  是我发明的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I invented that one
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定你会跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you can do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My leg
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来你可以带我回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess you can take me home now
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在你全都搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now that you've ruined everything
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭  有舞会专家在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:27.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, the prom expert is here
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来没弄砸过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:28.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I haven't failed yet
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can still
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  我弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:32.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I broke that
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:34.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭  别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, don't cry
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管做什么  别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you do, don't
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你对他做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.63,0:08:48.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What did you do to him?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可怜的小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Poor little guy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sponge, are you okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ruined everything
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你并没有完全搞砸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't mess everything up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,热狗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hot dog
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实热狗掉朱迪头发上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was pretty funny
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的还挺好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when that hot dog landed in Judy's hair
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只要你玩得开心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to have a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我的确玩得很开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I am having a good time
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道咱们舞还没跳完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, we haven't finished our dance yet
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还能戴假发吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:25.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I still wear the wig?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你还是可以戴假发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can still wear the wig
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:34.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(180.251,552)}舞曲
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  各位无脊椎动物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, you invertebrates
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要教你们怎么跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to teach you how to do the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快把腿抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you take your leg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再抬到半空中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and you stick it in the air
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再抬起另一条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you take the other one
Dialogue: 1,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后在那不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And jam it right up there
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转身转一周
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You twist yourself around
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后一顿猛扑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give a great big lunge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就是海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're doing the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.02,0:09:50.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Huh, do the sponge, sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.44,0:09:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, do the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定就在跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bet your buns you're doing the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要把腿抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now, first you take your leg
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再抬到半空中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:59.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you stick it in the air
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再抬起另一条腿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:03.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then you take the other one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后在那不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you jam it right up there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快滚  披萨顶料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get lost, pizza topping
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没看到我在跳海绵舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm doing the sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后一顿猛扑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and give a great big lunge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're doing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  这样就是海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now you're doing the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, do the sponge, sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, do the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知不觉你就入水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:24.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Before you know, you're taking the plunge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said the sponge, sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, do the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定就在跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bet your buns you're doing the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你肯定就在跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, bet your buns you're doing the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  这样就是海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, well, you're doing the sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(340.474,314)}主队
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1165.622,220)}客队
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, I said the sponge, sponge
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:39.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(835.162,712)}进球得分
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, do the sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳海绵舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, do the sponge, sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们爱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They love us
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're popular
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能去破坏别人的舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go wreck someone else's prom, will you?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee whiz, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉今晚没照着你的计划走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry tonight didn't turn out like you planned
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别担心了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道今晚会特别烂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it would be a total disaster all along
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过就烂而言  还真的很好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But as far as disasters go, that was really fun
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,离我的宝贝小花远点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:16.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep away from my precious little flower
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你差点就踩到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You almost stepped on it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  又矮又黄小海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, goodnight, short, yellow and spongy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good job, laddie
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在这啊  假人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, dummy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的好有用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure come in handy
