Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(414.577,538)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(216.301,368)}此处点餐
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.91,0:12:06.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:06.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:08.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘿  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我会咬钩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll bite
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道今天是什么日子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know what today is?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烦死章鱼哥日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Annoy Squidward day?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, silly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是15号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's on the 15th
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.51,0:12:21.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670.933,192)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today's the beginning of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:25.89,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(787.095,848)}本月最佳员工
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,评本月最佳员工了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the judging for employee of the month
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, don't you know
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个评奖都是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that award is a scam?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板给你评那个奖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:33.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs gives you that award
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就省得再加钱激励你努力工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so you'll work harder for no extra money
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样不对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is not true, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他给我评奖就是因为我努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He gives it to me because I work harder
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也可以赢到的  再努力点就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You could win it, too, if you tried harder
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,图什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:42.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我脸挂上耻辱墙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To get my face on the wall of shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572.797,190)}月度最佳员工
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  你这样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, you've got it all wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对自己的工作自豪没什么好耻辱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Having pride in your work is nothing to be ashamed of
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有一个东西能让一切变得值得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, it's the only thing that makes it all worthwhile
Dialogue: 1,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这样  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thattaboy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就是一场硬仗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is going to be a tough one, though
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有明确的赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:12:59.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no clear-cut winner
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out, SpongeBob--
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥似乎马上就要迎头赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward appears to be on the verge of a breakout
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346.482,652)}皱眉文摘
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个月的墙上估计就会有张新面孔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There might be a new face on the wall this month
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682.95,932)}一月
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's right, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我估计就要追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might sneak up on you
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:26.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我怎么会让工作质量退步这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could I have let the quality of my work slip so much?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,需要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Need some help?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making Krabby Patties?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都快失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're losing it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知不知道那个奖项就是堆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you know that award is a load of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,garbage
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别把这件事跟蟹老板说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, don't tell Mr. Krabs about this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样会影响到我评奖的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It'll hurt my chances of winning the award
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经跟你说过了  那奖项就是堆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:14.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already told you, that award is a bunch of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,baloney
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这话不对  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is not true, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟这顶帽子一样  这奖项代表着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like this hat, the award is a symbol of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代表着你是个傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a symbol that you're a chump
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而这个代表着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:27.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this is a symbol of
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我对于本月最佳员工奖的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:31.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what I think of the employee of the month award
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个有经验的本月最佳员工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,An experienced employee of the month
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总是会在帽子里放铅块
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,always keeps a brick of lead in his hat
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再跟你说最后一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you for the last time
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这奖项就只是个笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that award is nothing but a joke
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(696.969,896)}三月
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一章鱼哥说得对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if Squidward's right?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万一这奖项就是场骗局呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:49.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What if the award is a phony?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是不是表示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this mean
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有工作都没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my whole body of work is meaningless?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要再提那种言论  水手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.66,0:14:54.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stow that kind of talk, sailor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在这是场战争  列兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is war now, private
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是想要你有那么个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what he wants you to think
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们没时间再胆怯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is no time to go lily-livered on us
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是长官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,战争当中容不下可是  士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no room for "buts" in war, soldier
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他想让你崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.67,0:15:05.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wants you to crack
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在给你耍把戏  看透你的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's trying to trick you, get inside your mind
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You must stop at nothing--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I mean nothing--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击败他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:11.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to defeat him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说得够清楚了吗  列兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have I made myself clear, private?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清楚明白  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Crystal, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now move out
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能让章鱼哥赢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't let Squidward win
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.87,0:15:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是他起不来  他就上不了班了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can't go to work if he doesn't wake up
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,发现目标
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Target sighted
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:40.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没法起床上班就评不到奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't win that award if you don't get up for work
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住手  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我真的想评奖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I really wanted that award
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我爪子被绑起来我也能得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:08.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could win it with my tentacles tied
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就快安排上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That can be arranged
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你简直是疯了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a lunatic, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe so
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我本月最佳员工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I did win employee of the month
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经连赢26个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,26 months in a row
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are y
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是想说你比我强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to say that you are better than me?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经比你强了26个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been better than you for 26 months--
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天就是27个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it'll be 27 tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了  方块死脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, square-for-brains
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.15,0:17:27.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:27.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒要让你见识见识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to show you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,评上那奖有多简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how easy it is to win that award
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要当上新的本月最佳员工
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be the new employee of the month
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会证明给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:36.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will prove to you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能力比你强的多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am far more competent than you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很早就到蟹堡王给地板打蜡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going in early to wax the floors
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't bother
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你到的时候我早就打完蜡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have done it already by the time you get there
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你必须早起才能比我早到蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll have to get up pretty early
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.33,0:17:47.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get there before me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用不着睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need the sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.63,0:17:50.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:50.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Loser
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, me neither
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连输26次的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,26-time loser
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他  一直盯着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:01.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him, watching me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在盯着你呢  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm watching you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不可能比我早走的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not leaving before me
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  是不是很困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward, getting sleepy, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不困
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about you?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不困
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nighty-night
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:40.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我出去之后我就拧干你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to wring you dry when I get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get me out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下班后我会顺便来看看的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:52.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll stop by after work
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去休息休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:57.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to get some rest
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可别一脸劳累地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:18:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't want to look tired
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去拍本月最佳员工照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for my employee of the month photo
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样应该能拖住他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That ought to hold him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好你个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:33.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, you little
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(656.914,302)}失败大废物
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,永别了  海绵大废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, sponge loser
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.07,0:20:23.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:23.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Truce
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Truce
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I can't take it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If we keep this up
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都会评不到奖的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,neither of us will win the award
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该要留点力气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should save our energy for work
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做好我们分内的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where we really need it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.55,0:20:42.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  那就来场干净的较量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:42.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's have a good, clean fight
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁能力强谁就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:44.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And may the better man win
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是个谎话连篇毫无骨气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's nothing but a lying, boneless
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又喷墨又鼻子大的大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ink-squirting, big-nosed phony
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看那又露龅牙又俗套的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that buck-toothed, corn-fed smile
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他这人可一点都信不得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't trust him as far as you can throw him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到他把我手一握完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As soon as he stops shaking my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就赶快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make a run for it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:13.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(226.315,366)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钱  钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Money, money
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要去赚点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,going to make some money
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(142.198,924)}入口
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能看到我员工来这么早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It warms me wallet to see me employees
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我钱包都暖化了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coming in so early
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们来得可真早
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys, you're early
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板你看  扫地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. Krabs, clean floors
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擦桌子  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:40.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean tables, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,洗盘子  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:44.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clean dishes, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.74,0:21:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么洗盘子才更高效  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's more efficient to clean dishes this way, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.08,0:21:55.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送你的花朵跟巧克力  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flowers and chocolates for you, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.12,0:21:56.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:56.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把我自己的钱放收银机了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm putting my own money into the register, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.29,0:22:04.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用两把锅铲能提高生产效率  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:04.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two spatulas to increase productivity, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Faster, SpongeBob, faster
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.97,0:22:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翻肉饼压根不算什么事  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.97,0:22:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to this patty flipping, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我产量轻轻松松就能到你两倍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll easily double your output
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵小员工
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.30,0:22:12.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sponge cog
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.43,0:22:16.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.43,0:22:16.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.35,0:22:18.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:18.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:20.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Help
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.45,0:22:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.45,0:22:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  有蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:37.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走  你们必须要付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, you've got to pay for those
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.71,0:22:40.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.71,0:22:40.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:41.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.54,0:22:42.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:42.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys, the Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到底谁评上了本月最佳员工
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So who's the winner of employee of the month?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:48.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人  蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys, the Krabby Patties
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.72,0:22:52.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:52.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys, wait
